text: <Limited time only, special project! >"Hello! It's Hachan" is updated with the super fantastic episode 8! That "Hachan" is animated! Hachan" is now animated! In response to your enthusiastic support, we will update it for a little while longer!
This time "Hachan" is preparing for Halloween. Not only preparing for the costume, but also practicing that song...will "Hachan" be able to master the popular song? Don't miss the special costume!
